spec_data.Name: ini4j
spec_data.Description:
ini4j is a simple Java API for handling configuration files in Windows
.ini format. Additionally, the library includes Java Preferences API
implementation based on the .ini file.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 26 Jul 2017 05:44:38 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Java API for handling files in Windows .ini format
